rows.label: qev300001_MSG0001
rows.name:
You the BLADE who accepted our miranium delivery
request?[ST:wait ]

rows.label: qev300001_MSG0002
rows.name: Great. Have you got the 700 units of miranium?[ST:wait ]

rows.label: qev300001_SEL0021
rows.name: Hold on to your miranium for now.[ST:wait ]

rows.label: qev300001_MSG0004
rows.name: Thanks. Hopefully we can do this again sometime.[ST:wait ]

rows.label: qev300001_MSG0005
rows.name:
Well, I can't force you. Hope you change your mind
soon, though.[ST:wait ]

rows.label: qev300001_MSG0006
rows.name: Uh-oh. Looks like you're shy of the full 700 units.[ST:wait ]
